    </h2>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      <span class="govuk-caption-m">Last 30 days</span>
      <span class="govuk-caption-m">+25% from last month</span>
    </p>
    <details class="govuk-details">
      <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
        <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">
          How do we measure submission rate?
        </span>
      </summary>
      <div class="govuk-details__text">
        A completed notification is one that has been submitted to <abbr title="Office for Product Safety and Standards">OPSS</abbr> for review, and is not a draft.
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>

